<p><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/table_text_content.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/table_text_content.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"677\" height=\"257\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',10,'ENG','Optional','<p class=\"title\">Optional tables</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This is the set of optional tables to have extra features of your &lt;isym:lisha/&gt; object.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">There is tree part of optional features to provide you :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>User documentation</li>\n<li>Technical documentation</li>\n<li>Ticket changelog list</li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',11,'ENG','user documentation','<p class=\"title\">User documentation tables</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">User documentation needs two tables.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Main node&nbsp;table is&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_doc_user/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n<li>Caption details with localization is&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_doc_user_caption/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">SQL script</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">CREATE TABLE</span> IF NOT EXISTS <span style=\"color: #008000;\">`&lt;isys:table_config/&gt;`</span> (</em><br /><em> <span style=\"color: #008000;\">`id`</span> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">int</span>(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT <span style=\"color: #008000;\">\'key identifier number\'</span>,</em><br /><em> <span style=\"color: #008000;\">`value`</span> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">varchar</span>(200) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">NOT NULL</span> COMMENT <span style=\"color: #008000;\">\'Value of configuration\'</span>,</em><br /><em> <span style=\"color: #008000;\">`unite`</span> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">varchar</span>(15) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">NOT NULL</span> COMMENT <span style=\"color: #008000;\">\'Unit of configuration value\'</span>,</em><br /><em> <span style=\"color