ad Write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Possible values</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span> : means you will create the link to ticket list.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/ticket_list.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/ticket_list.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"381\" height=\"179\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">False</span>&nbsp;: means you will not create any link.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Pre requisite</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Feature &lt;ipage:15 ???????/&gt;have to be set to <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_ticket</span>\'<span>, </span><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span><span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Your cursor will turn into active link when you fly over&nbsp;&lt;ipage:15 <span>Application version/&gt;.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_ticket</span>\'<span>, </span><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span><span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Nothing special appends</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Read</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_ticket_link</span>\'<span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>will return&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tickets screen</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/tickets_list.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/tickets_list.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"222\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',22,'ENG','user documentation : [color=CadetBlue]__active_user_doc[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Fonction</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Display or hide button to go to user documentation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Name</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_user_doc</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Read Write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div class=\"icon_doc_user\" style=\"float: left; display: block; height: 20px; width: 20px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Possible values</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span> : Display button to reach user documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/user_doc_button.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/user_doc_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"305\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">False</span>&nbsp;: No button displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_user_doc</span>\'<span>, </span><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span><span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span class=\"subtitle\">Read</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"c