style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active</span><span style=\"color: #008080;\">_tech_doc</span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">will return <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></p>'),('MT0.10',24,'ENG','Core','<p class=\"title\">Overview</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Set of internal features</p>'),('MT0.10',25,'ENG','main query : [color=CadetBlue]__main_query[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Fonction</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Define main query to draw in &lt;ipage:20/&gt; of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Definition of main query is important step in two parts.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Define fields you have to display</li>\n<li>Have a good writing formalization&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Standard</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">__main_query</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Read Write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Possible values</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">A string that define a query.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">$query</span> <span>= \"</span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">`TRAN`.`id`<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `id`,&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">`TRAN`.`daterec`<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `daterec`,</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">`TRAN`.`description`<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `description`,&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 120px;\">`TRAN`.`amount`<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `amount`</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 90px;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">FROM</span>&nbsp;`transaction` `TRAN`&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 90px;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE</span> 1 = 1\"; <span style=\"color: #888888;\">-- Mandatory part</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__main_query</span>\'<span>, </span><span style=\"color: #808080;\">$query</span><span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span class=\"subtitle\">Read</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(</span>\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__main_query</span>\'<span>);</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>will return query defined above</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No default value, it\'s a <strong>mandatory</strong> feature !</p>'),('MT0.10',26,'ENG','Navigation bar','<p class=\"title\">Overview</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">The body screen part display navigation bar.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have both top and bottom navigation bar.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/navigation_bar_overview.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/navigation_bar_overview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"855\" height=\"311\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',27,'ENG','Number of lines by page : [color=CadetBlue]define_nb_line[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Define maximum number of lines to draw on each page.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">define_nb_line</span>(<em>p_nb_line</em>, <em>p_selected_lines</em> = 